	<entry xml:lang="en">
		<title type="html">(Modified) Maximumize and Minimumize</title>
		<link href="http://edgurgel.wordpress.com/2008/10/29/modified-maximumize-and-minimumize/"/>
		<id>http://edgurgel.wordpress.com/?p=12</id>
		<updated>2008-10-29T23:41:47+00:00</updated>
		<content type="html">&lt;div class=&quot;snap_preview&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;p&gt;Marco Diego(Marcola) and Eduardo Gurgel(me) were thinking about how improve window management on Compiz-Fusion. We decided to work on it modifying Maximumize and creating Minimumize.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;First we modified Maximumize plugin to maximumize on any direction. Later, we created Minimumize plugin that allows the user to set the window to half the size in a specified direction. Hard to imagine? Watch the videos:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://edgurgel.wordpress.com/2008/10/29/modified-maximumize-and-minimumize/&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://img.youtube.com/vi/35M2sVYRVuY/2.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
