		<content type="html">&lt;div class=&quot;snap_preview&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Patches are almost finished&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;So I&amp;#8217;ve finished what I wanted to achieve with input redirection and the X patches, now I just need to do a little bugfixing and hole-filling. The only things I haven&amp;#8217;t got around to doing are expo and wiitrack, mainly because they were too complicated for me to implement in the current system.&lt;/p&gt;
